@startuml sequence_append_inference
title Sequence Diagram - Luồng append CSV + inference fraud

autonumber
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #334155
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #0F766E
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #ECFDF5

actor "Người dùng" as User
boundary "Frontend\nCsvUploadPanel" as FE
control "Backend\nCsv2GraphController" as Controller
control "Csv2GraphService" as Csv2Graph
control "DatasetMetaService" as MetaService
control "FeatureService" as Feature
control "DataPtService" as DataPt
control "GnnInferenceService" as GnnInference
control "Python GNN Service" as GnnService
control "Neo4jIngestService" as Ingest
database "Neo4j" as Neo4j
collections "Metadata Cache\n_latest_[database].json\n_raw_[database].json" as Meta
collections "Model File\nfgnn_star.pt" as Model

User -> FE: Upload CSV mới\nkhông có is_fraud
FE -> Controller: POST /csv2graph/run
Controller -> Csv2Graph: run(file, dto)
Csv2Graph -> MetaService: loadLatest(database)
MetaService -> Meta: Đọc metadata dataset
Meta --> MetaService: nodeLabel, schema, targetLabel, hasModel
MetaService --> Csv2Graph: meta

Csv2Graph -> Neo4j: countNodes(nodeLabel)
Neo4j --> Csv2Graph: existingNodes > 0
Csv2Graph -> Csv2Graph: Chọn APPEND mode
Csv2Graph -> MetaService: loadRawInfo(database)
MetaService -> Meta: Đọc raw columns gốc
Meta --> MetaService: rawColumns
MetaService --> Csv2Graph: RawInfo

Csv2Graph -> Csv2Graph: Parse CSV + validate columns
Csv2Graph -> Feature: Encode theo schema cũ
Feature --> Csv2Graph: encodedRows
Csv2Graph -> DataPt: buildDataPt(jobDir, inference)
DataPt --> Csv2Graph: data.pt

Csv2Graph -> GnnInference: predictDataPt(data.pt)
GnnInference -> GnnService: POST /predict-data-pt
GnnService -> Model: Load fgnn_star.pt
GnnService --> GnnInference: scores + predicted labels
GnnInference --> Csv2Graph: prediction

Csv2Graph -> Csv2Graph: Gán nhãn is_fraud vào rows mới
Csv2Graph -> Ingest: ingest(rows đã gán nhãn,\nMERGE mode)
Ingest -> Neo4j: MERGE nodes + relationships
Neo4j --> Ingest: Ingest stats
Ingest --> Csv2Graph: OK

Csv2Graph --> Controller: response.inference
Controller --> FE: Append success
FE --> User: Toast số fraud dự đoán\nvà cập nhật graph

@enduml
